Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Engineer I role with Axon. I bring over three years of experience building backend systems, workflow orchestration, and data services in *Java*, *Python*, *Spring Boot*, *FastAPI*, *PostgreSQL*, *Redis*, and *AWS*, along with a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

At Sperse, I built a *multi-agent* CRM platform in *Python*, *FastAPI*, *LangGraph*, and *LangChain* for *10,000+ users*, routing requests across *40+ specialized sub-agents* as a *web-scale data system* while partnering with *Product and Design* to ship *end-to-end features*. I also owned *architecture design meetings* for a *React Flow* and *TypeScript* workflow builder backed by *Temporal* for durable, resumable execution, built an agentic *code reviews* pipeline integrating *OpenAI Codex* with a custom *Bitbucket MCP* server to triage *25–30 PRs/week*, created a *FastMCP* server exposing *160+ backend actions*, and shipped GitHub Actions *CI/CD* with OpenTelemetry trace-based evals to protect quality and performance. At Qualitest, I designed a cloud-agnostic Storage Service in *Java* and *Spring Boot* with *PostgreSQL* and *Redis*, turning *SQL* and *NoSQL* data stores into one backend surface across *Google Cloud Storage*, *S3*, and *MinIO*, then optimized *PostgreSQL* and orchestrated *100K+* weekly jobs with *AWS Step Functions* for *high throughput* and *high availability*. That combination maps directly to Axon’s need for engineers who can own *end-to-end features*, participate in *code reviews* and *architecture design meetings*, and make data accessible and actionable.

Axon’s mission to *Protect Life*, and its focus on *Preserve Truth* and *Accelerate Justice*, strongly resonates with me. I am drawn to the opportunity to help build software that supports public safety decisions, and I value the kind of *cross-team collaboration* and rigorous engineering culture that your software team emphasizes. I would welcome the chance to contribute my backend and data-systems experience to this mission and help Axon protect more lives in more places. Thank you for your consideration; I can be reached at #ph or #eml.

